body:
Old tracks that I made (which are nooby) that I want to share. Expect them to be repetitive and annoying, but regardless I put effort into it. Mainly focusing on finishing up the tracks to release them, but since most of them are old they are... less improved. I've done a lot of reevaluating on my work and moving to FL, so just wanted to drop my music stuff below. More coming soon (older ofc)

#1 - Neoletrik (Soft, electro feel with a little spice to it.)
#2 - Miliwrath (This has to be my oldest track. I don't know what it is but I finished it with the lyric txt.)
#3 - Demolition (Trance, bit repetitive but has it's peaks.)
